	</div><!--/.embed-container-->
	
		<div class="video_embed_content">In November of 2012, Roger Goodell, Commissioner of the National Football League, spoke about player safety in both the NFL and youth sports at The Dean&#8217;s Distinguished Lecture at HSPH.</div>
		
